Name:           Lsl
version:        0.1
Synopsis:	execution and testing framework for Linden Scripting Language (LSL)
Description:	
	Provides a framework for executing Linden Scripting Language scripts 'offline',
	e.g. outside a Second Life simulator.  Includes a quasiquotation parser for LSL,
	a simulation of Second Life (a simulated simulator), and a unit testing framework.
	Also provides the LslPlus executable, for use with the LslPlus Eclips plugin.
